#: ../../S/Saturday-night-special.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from police slang for a cheap handgun] A :ref:`quick-and-dirty` program or "
"feature kluged together during off hours, under a deadline, and in response "
"to pressure from a :ref:`salescritter`\\. Such hacks are dangerously "
"unreliable, but all too often sneak into a production release after "
"insufficient review."
msgstr ""
"[安物の拳銃を指す警察の俗語から] 締め切りに追われ、\\ :ref:`salescritter`\\ からの圧力に応じて、業務時間外に\\ "
":ref:`quick-and-dirty`\\ "
"に寄せ集められたプログラムや機能。そうしたハックは危険なほど信頼性に欠けるが、不十分なレビューのまま本番リリースに紛れ込むことがあまりにも多い。"
